      &lt;img alt="An illustration of Universal’s Epic Universe park opening in May 2025." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ntkq03xU6WkTg2gyGrt4HsrImPw=/56x0:823x511/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73659772/Screenshot_2024_10_17_at_11.02.15.0.png" /&gt;
